data.description: Welcome to the quaint neighborhood of Glenbrook East, nestled off of La Riviera. This charming 3bedroom/2bathroom updated home exudes comfort and is conveniently located. The open-beam living room boasts a fireplace along with a vaulted ceiling. There is a bonus room off of the kitchen and Living room which could be a Family Room, Game Room, Dining space, office space, or whatever you dream of! The beautifully updated kitchen features a breakfast bar, along with eat in kitchen space. The primary suite features 2 closets along with an updated bathroom with a stand up shower and double sinks. The driveway is extra wide along with space for a car, boat or possible RV behind the double gate. The backyard has ample space. Conveniently located near the scenic American River Parkway, California State University Sacramento (CSUS), and a short commute to downtown Sacramento, this home offers the ideal blend of privacy and urban convenience. The roof and HVAC were all replaced in 2017, Kitchen and Bathrooms were updated in the last 6 months, water heater is newer as well. The  Vinyl sliding windows are double glazed and the home has a Thermal coating paint on the exterior that helps reduce heating and cooling costs which was also done in 2017. Come make this your new home!
